1356:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c **** /**
1357:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Return the SYSCLK frequency.
1358:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *
1359:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   The system frequency computed by this function may not be the real
1360:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         frequency in the chip. It is calculated based on the predefined
1361:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         constants of the selected clock source:
1362:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is HSI, function returns values based on HSI_VALUE(*)
1363:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is CSI, function returns values based on CSI_VALUE(**)
1364:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is HSE, function returns values based on HSE_VALUE(***)
1365:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     If SYSCLK source is PLL, function returns values based on HSI_VALUE(*), CSI_VALUE(**)
1366:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *           or HSE_VALUE(***) multiplied/divided by the PLL factors.
1367:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     (*) HSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32h5xx_hal_conf.h file (default value
1368:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *               64 MHz) but the real value may vary depending on the variations
1369:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *               in voltage and temperature.
1370:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     (**) CSI_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32h5xx_hal_conf.h file (default value
1371:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *               4 MHz) but the real value may vary depending on the variations
1372:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *               in voltage and temperature.
1373:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note     (***) HSE_VALUE is a constant defined in stm32h5xx_hal_conf.h file (default value
1374:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *                24 MHz), user has to ensure that HSE_VALUE is same as the real
1375:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *                frequency of the crystal used. Otherwise, this function may
1376:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *                have wrong result.
1377:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *
1378:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   The result of this function could be not correct when using fractional
1379:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         value for HSE crystal.
1380:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *
1381:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   This function can be used by the user application to compute the
