1739:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c **** /**
1740:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @brief  Configure the RCC item(s) attribute(s).
1741:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   Available attributes are to secure items and set RCC as privileged (*).
1742:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         Default state is non-secure and unprivileged access allowed.
1743:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   Secure and non-secure attributes can only be set from the secure
1744:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         state when the system implements the security (TZEN=1).
1745:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @note   As the privileged attributes concern either all secure or all non-secure
1746:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         RCC resources accesses and not each RCC individual items access attribute,
1747:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         the application must ensure that the privilege access attribute configurations
1748:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         are coherent amongst the security level set on RCC individual items
1749:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         so not to overwrite a previous more restricted access rule (consider either
1750:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         all secure and/or all non-secure RCC resources accesses by privileged-only
1751:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         transactions or privileged and unprivileged transactions).
1752:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @param  Item Item(s) to set attributes on.
1753:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         This parameter can be a one or a combination of @ref RCC_items (**).
1754:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @param  Attributes specifies the RCC secure/privilege attributes.
1755:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *         This parameter can be a value of  @ref RCC_attributes
1756:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * @retval None
1757:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   *
1758:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * (*)   : For stm32h503xx devices, attributes specifies the privilege attribute only (no items).
1759:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   * (**)  : For stm32h503xx devices, this parameter is unused, it can take 0 or any other numerical
1760:Drivers/STM32H5xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h5xx_hal_rcc.c ****   */
